nodes.text: Timothy S. Maddocks wrote the story of Janus Greejatus appearing in the Databank, through the What's the Story? feature of Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club. He is known as "vader_of_bast" on Starwars.com.
His alias is The_Four_Dot_Elipsis on TheForce.net, and he is also a former administrator on Wookieepedia, where he is known as Thefourdotelipsis.
